Muchidzidzo [[fundoyetsimba]], [[mhanda]] (Force) tinoiwona mazuva ose panosundwa kana kuzvuviwa chinhu. Fosi inokenzera kuchinja kwemmuchacha (speed), kuchinja kwedzivo, kana kuchinja kwemaumbirwo akaita chiumbwa Shape)zvikuru sei takatarisana nezviumbwa zvisina kusimba. Fosi ine tsazaniso (equation) inoti F = huremu X kufangura. Fosi inopimwa nechiyero chinonzi Newton (N).
